                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When the hellbound honor guard is reduced to 0 Hit Points, a fiery fissure forms beneath their feet and a host of screeching devils pours forth to drag their souls to Hell. All creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] take 3d8 fire and @Damage[3d8[spirit]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:29|basic] save), and all creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] must attempt a @Check[will|dc:29] save or be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2} on a critical failure). The rift then immediately closes.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
