                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The honor guard strikes with their maces against enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5], battering souls as well as bodies (@Check[reflex|dc:29|basic] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d6+1)[bludgeoning],1d6[spirit]|options:area-damage]{1d6+1 bludgeoning damage plus 1d6 spirit damage}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d6+9)[bludgeoning],2d6[spirit]|options:area-damage]{2d6+9 bludgeoning damage plus 2d6 spirit damage}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d6+12)[bludgeoning],2d6[spirit]|options:area-damage]{3d6+12 bludgeoning damage plus 2d6 spirit damage}</p>"
                },
