                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The hellbound honor guard has only 2 segments</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> On the edge of defeat, the honor guard calls a paean to Asmodeus for aid. The honor guard regains @Damage[3d8[healing]] Hit Points. As standard for troops reduced to 2 segments, they can't regain Hit Points above the lowest listed threshold.</p>"
                },
